            "title": "Basic Math Operations ➕",
            "content": "# Arithmetic in Python\n\n| Operator | Meaning | Example |\n|----------|---------|----------|\n| `+` | Addition | `5 + 3 = 8` |\n| `-` | Subtraction | `5 - 3 = 2` |\n| `*` | Multiplication | `5 * 3 = 15` |\n| `/` | Division | `5 / 3 = 1.67` |\n\nPython can do all basic math!"
