            "id": "s_l3_7",
            "type": "text",
            "title": "Special Division Operators ➗",
            "content": "# Beyond Basic Division\n\n* **`/`** — True division (always float)\n  * `7 / 2 = 3.5`\n* **`//`** — Floor division (integer result)\n  * `7 // 2 = 3`\n* **`%`** — Modulo (remainder)\n  * `7 % 2 = 1`"
        },
        {
            "id": "s_l3_8",
            "type": "code",
            "title": "Division Types 💻",
            "content": "Compare the three division operations:",
            "codeSnippet": "print(\"7 / 2 =\", 7 / 2)   # True division\nprint(\"7 // 2 =\", 7 // 2) # Floor division\nprint(\"7 % 2 =\", 7 % 2)   # Remainder\n\n# Practical: hours and minutes\ntotal_minutes = 135\nhours = total_minutes // 60\nminutes = total_minutes % 60\nprint(f\"{hours} hours and {minutes} minutes\")",
            "codeLanguage": "python",
            "canRunCode": true
        },
