            "title": "Exponentiation 📈",
            "content": "# Powers in Python\n\nUse `**` for exponentiation (powers):\n\n```python\n2 ** 3 = 8     # 2 to the power of 3\n10 ** 2 = 100  # 10 squared\n9 ** 0.5 = 3.0 # Square root!\n```\n\nThis works with any numbers, including decimals!"
        },
