            "title": "Order of Operations 📐",
            "content": "# PEMDAS in Python\n\nPython follows math order of operations:\n\n1. **P**arentheses `( )`\n2. **E**xponents `**`\n3. **M**ultiplication & **D**ivision `* / // %`\n4. **A**ddition & **S**ubtraction `+ -`\n\n```python\n2 + 3 * 4 = 14    # Not 20!\n(2 + 3) * 4 = 20  # Parentheses first\n```"
